<br>
<br>
Please keep in mind that this is not a defenitive list of all the best cards in the set, it is just my opinion of which rare cards are the most playable, and which ones you should be on the lookout for when trading or buying cards. If you think I forget a rare that deserves to be on the list. or if you think one of the ones I listed doesn&#39;t belong there, d-mail me and I&#39;ll see what I can do.<br>
<br>
Thanks for reading,<br>
